window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>&nbsp;Allie Harris wants payback.&nbsp;</b></p> <p>Her cheating ex deserves to see her living her best life; a one-night-stand with a hot South African soccer player would be the perfect revenge. Right? <br> &nbsp;</p> <p>Wrong. Allie is so, so wrong. <br> &nbsp;</p> <p><b>Roan Dewalt has all the moves.&nbsp;</b></p> <p>On and off the field he’s at the top of his game. Roan respects hard work, dedication, and follow through. He’s not a one-and-done kind of man, and he’s far from being done with Allie Harris. <br> &nbsp;</p> <p>One sexy night and two years later, Allie’s job brings her back to town. An opportunity for the perfect replay Roan has been fantasizing about since they slept together.&nbsp;</p> <p><b>The problem?&nbsp;</b></p> <p>Allie Harris has a secret, one she’s been keeping from Roan all this time. Video proof of their one night together taken without his consent. <br> &nbsp;</p> <p>Will Allie’s payback plan come back to bite them both? Or can she erase her past mistake and embrace a new future with Roan?</p>"; 
